{"tid":1543894,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"總之跳閘就唔啱啦","createTime":"2019-09-05T11:04:28.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-05T12:40:37.000Z","uid":142127,"like":17,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"7c6330672dc3cbb004f87ae73c154672743eae72","tid":1543894,"uid":142127,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T11:04:28.000Z","msg":"Sorry for 標題黨<br />\n話說呢排跳閘無咁多中年人支持<br />\n多數都係覺得呢樣野係唔啱<br />\n但係我同我老母講跳閘係班狗仔教我地架喎 點解唔啱<br />\n之後再show張gif比佢睇<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3zY91Xf.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3zY91Xf.gif&h=c1baf80d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n我老母：哦⋯⋯唔怪得知啦 咁我都跳先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n最後佢返工啲同事講到跳閘係唔啱<br />\n佢用左同一個方法去解釋<br />\n最後佢成班同事都決定開始要跳閘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f5c81db90c4e20d87f49b4a101475c1d781542ea","tid":1543894,"uid":317299,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T11:10:59.000Z","msg":"[行動post] 出咗不反對啦！【9月6 反濫捕 抗威權 遮打集會】<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1543083\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1543083</a><br />\n<br />\n[置頂]9.6遮打反濫暴抗威權集會 已獲批不反對通知書<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/agyFBwU\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/agyFBwU</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/KTsuWvi.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKTsuWvi.jpg&h=59781468&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Ud9tv0z.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUd9tv0z.jpg&h=17d13451&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wcJFfrO.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FwcJFfrO.jpg&h=7f9dd8d5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/TjeJddu.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTjeJddu.jpg&h=e690fd03&s={SI